Package data.trainnetwork

Class Summary
BookableSection A Section allowing seat reservations
Network A DefaultDirectedWeightedGraph representing the Train network
Route An object describing a train route
Seat A class representing a Seat within section
Section An Edge representing a path between two train Stations being part of a train line
SectionInfo An object containing a section and some additional detail
Station A Vertex representing a train Station in the network

Exception Summary
NoSuchSeatException An exception thrown when trying to access a non-existing Seat
NoSuchSectionException Exception thrown when trying to access a Seat in a BookableSection that does not exist
SectionFullException An exception thrown when trying to access Section functionalities requiring free Seats, however no more are available
